==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overseer
<hw>O`ver*seer"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who oversees;
a superintendent; a supervisor; <as>as, an <ex>overseer</ex> of a
mill</as>; specifically, one or certain public officers; <as>as, an
<ex>overseer</ex> of the poor; an <ex>overseer</ex> of
highways.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overseership</ent>⟦br⟧
